OL,3,CPothole plague: frustrated motorists
OL,4,Ccall for long-term repairs to damaged
OL,5,Croads
OL,7,FDrivers are calling for more to be
OL,8,Fdone to deal with a 'plague of
OL,9,Fpotholes' across roads in the South.
OL,10,FThe call for more action comes on
OL,11,FNational Pothole Day, which falls on
OL,12,Fthe 15th of January every year.
OL,14,FThey say not enough is being done to
OL,15,Frepair potholes, and quick fixes just
OL,16,Fmake the problem worse.
