OL,3,CPothole plague: frustrated motorists
OL,4,Ccall for long-term repairs to damaged
OL,5,Croads
OL,7,FThe Pothole Partnership was formed two
OL,8,Fyears ago by the AA, JCB, British
OL,9,FCycling and the National Motorcyclists
OL,10,FCouncil. It is calling for a shift in
OL,11,Fhow local authorities approach
OL,12,Frepairs, as it says money is being
OL,13,Fwasted on short-term fixes.
OL,15,FIt says that in many cases, the same
OL,16,Fsections of road are revisited within
OL,17,Fa year as previous repairs fail. The
OL,18,Fgroup wants to see the introduction of
OL,19,Fa minimum five-year warranty on every
OL,20,Fnon-emergency pothole repair.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
