OL,3,CPothole plague: frustrated motorists
OL,4,Ccall for long-term repairs to damaged
OL,5,Croads
OL,7,FNew data underlines the scale of the
OL,8,Fproblem as drivers across England can
OL,9,Fnow see how well their local highway
OL,10,Fauthority is tackling the pothole
OL,11,Fplague after a new traffic light
OL,12,Frating system was published by the
OL,13,Fgovernment.
OL,15,FRed, amber and green ratings now grade
OL,16,Fcouncils based on the current road
OL,17,Fcondition, so motorists can see if
OL,18,Fthey are fixing potholes effectively.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
