OL,3,CPothole plague: frustrated motorists
OL,4,Ccall for long-term repairs to damaged
OL,5,Croads
OL,7,FThe system takes into account the
OL,8,Fcondition of local roads, how much the
OL,9,Flocal authority is spending on road
OL,10,Frepairs and whether they are following
OL,11,Fbest practice in maintaining highways.
OL,13,FThe Department of Transport says the
OL,14,Frecord #7.3 billion to fix roads that
OL,15,Fwas announced in the budget means a
OL,16,Fmove away from expensive, short-term
OL,17,Frepairs towards investment in long-
OL,18,Fterm preventative measures.
